# Cloudflare Pages — URL redirects
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Format: /from /to [status]
# Status defaults to 301 (permanent). Use 302 for temporary, 200 for
# rewrites (proxy).
#
# Phase 1: empty. Real redirects appear in Phase 2+ as URLs evolve.
# Examples we'll likely add:
#   - /designers /designers/  301      (trailing slash normalization)
#   - /old-product-slug /new-product-slug 301
#   - /home / 301                       (defensive against legacy links)
